abstract: South Korean military announces North Korea launched several short-range projectiles from port city of Hamhung into sea between Korean Peninsula and Japan.
lead_paragraph: The projectiles, launched from the east coast, landed in the sea between the Korean Peninsula and Japan, the South Korean military said.

headline.main: North Korea Launches Short-Range Projectiles, Seoul Says
headline.print_headline: World Briefing | Asia; North Korea: Projectiles Fired Into Sea
